name: RavensFlashBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: The Baltimore Ravens Flash Briefing keeps fans connected with the team 365 days a year. Featuring daily updates from team writers, fans can catch up on the day’s biggest topics, including the latest news, injury reports, transactions, gameday info, team events and more. End each day with everything you need to know about the Ravens.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
